Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷口那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然說要在那家便利商店打工
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前在烤肉店打工的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上的女孩子辭職後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也立刻就放手不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沒吃夠苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟他是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子能好好讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧長門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圖書館門請保持安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我預期中的更喜歡這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 長門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來已經高興得手足無措了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說是厲害的集中力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道她會這麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早點帶她過來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 喜歡看書的是現在的長門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於願意停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 長門 我們是來讀書的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲毫不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看她那麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼好意思讓她停下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那邊等你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看夠了再過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝倉打過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種壓迫感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了你接了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和長門在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一起的話就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她還沒回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是愛操心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是辛苦啊 這位媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天毫無成果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我這邊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在去找長門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連教科書都沒翻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 一動不動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經閉館了回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 把書放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看到能罷手的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再給我十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遺憾 十分鐘後就關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就九分鐘 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真會擠時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你擺出那副表情也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快點辦張卡借走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶了卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帶了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你那麼不願鬆手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為沒有帶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才想起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那就無可厚非了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那趕快借一借回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想起來之前我都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是以前的長門有希和他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初遇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書給我 你要辦借書卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在和你說話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想辦借書卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫你辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 就是這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用不用 我反而要為擅自做主而道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為身邊有這種讓人操心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就沒辦法無視需要幫助的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿不到書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是讓我操心的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許這麼大聲地叫別人的外號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不許學貓叫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能道謝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐的準備還需要些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去換衣服洗臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在夢裏 我凝視著她的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點一點地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我體門沉睡著的她的人格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許在一點一點地甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她完全甦醒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 現在的這個我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會怎樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是特價日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了我們就去圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要好好讀書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 有點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那就趕快搞定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 你先去圖書館也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我一個人去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會睡著 又會睡著 絕對會睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣呢 要帶著回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了那我把這個放到盒子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡修好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很合適吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要好好讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很在意你剛才的停頓…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 這只是我的請求而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很對不起長門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能在身邊幫我陪我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門 這題…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個代入的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了 謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個我不會的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 長門也會有不會做的問題…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找找有沒有什麼可以參考的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不會的就立刻叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得今天的我有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我要拒絕戴上她的眼鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我會對他過於關注？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這鼓動的速度會變快？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數據不足無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,契機是在夢裏看到她以前的記憶 這個沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的人格在漸漸的覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我現在擁有的不可思議的感覺也是她的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是我 雖說我擁有她的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感情和感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在所認識的情報、經驗都是我自己的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些都是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的意識跟我的意識混合在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著她覺醒的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會跟我的混在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼在她完全覺醒的時侯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可能會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那時候將會發生什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門同學解不了的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說我來幫忙有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但至少這種小事我能幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿好你的書
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是多管閒事 褒義的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好是褒義的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我只是自己看不下去而已」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊對對對 就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？我有跟你說過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像久違的看到長門的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是加上那時候的那份感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時侯？哪個時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 先趁熱來一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要現在吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:19:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 不是不可以不是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請慢吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅是呆呆的觀望著他們的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單純的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單純的…夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是魔法什麼的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…只是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺能摸到 卻又摸不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛那個是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 她的人格照這樣慢慢的覺醒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會…我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失

